<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to SkillBridge!</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2ecc71 0%, #27ae60 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 15px 30px; background: #2ecc71; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
        .feature { background: white; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #2ecc71; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Welcome to SkillBridge!</h1>
            <h2>Your journey starts now, {{name}}!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Congratulations! Your email has been verified and your SkillBridge account is now active.</p>
            
            {{#if (eq userType "Student")}}
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>ðŸŽ“ For Students</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Browse internships and entry-level positions</li>
                    <li>Connect with leading companies and startups</li>
                    <li>Build your professional profile</li>
                    <li>Apply to opportunities that match your skills</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{else}}
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>ðŸ’¼ For Employers</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Post internship and job opportunities</li>
                    <li>Access talented undergraduate students</li>
                    <li>Build your company brand on campus</li>
                    <li>Connect with the next generation of talent</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <p>Ready to get started?</p>
            <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
            
            <hr style="margin: 30px 0;">
            <h3>Next Steps:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Complete your profile with all relevant information</li>
                <li>Upload a professional profile picture</li>
                {{#if (eq userType "Student")}}
                <li>Add your skills, projects, and academic achievements</li>
                <li>Start browsing and applying to opportunities</li>
                {{else}}
                <li>Add your company information and verify your business</li>
                <li>Post your first job or internship opportunity</li>
                {{/if}}
            </ol>
            
            <p>If you have any questions, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help getting started? Visit our <a href="{{loginUrl}}">Help Center</a></p>
